StoredProcedureSqlServerv2k5.name: [GetAllDutyPreference]
StoredProcedureSqlServerv2k5.body:
AS
SELECT dp.[DUTY_PREFERENCE_CODE] AS Code, dp.[DUTY_PREFERENCE_DESCRIPTION] AS Descrip.on, pdp.[PROGRAM_CODE] AS ProgramTypeCode FROM [dbo].[DUTY_PREFERENCE] dp WITH (NOLOCK) INNER JOIN [PROGRAM_DUTY_PREFERENCE] pdp on dp.[DUTY_PREFERENCE_CODE] = pdp.[DUTY_PREFERENCE_CODE] ORDER BY DUTY_PREFERENCE_DESCRIPTION
